<body>
<DIV id="gascalc">
 <img id="gas-pump" src="http://www.congoworld.com/images/gas_pump.gif" alt="Save up to 11% in gas mileage with a Tonneau Cover!" />
 <H3>TONNEAU COVERS SAVE UP TO 11% IN FUEL COSTS - CALCULATE YOURS NOW!</H3>

 <form id="mpgcalc" name="form1" action="" method=post>
   <label class="cost">Cost Per Gallon </label>
     <input name="gallon" type="text" id="gallon" size="8" maxlength="4" />
  <br />
   <label class="mpg2">Your Truck's mpg</label>
     <input name="mpg" type="text" id="mpg" size="8" maxlength="2" />
   <br />
   <label class="miles">Annual miles drive</label>
     <input name="milesdriven" type="text" id="milesdriven" size="8" maxlength="8" />
 <p id="mfs">Monthly Fuel Savings: <span id="savings2">&nbsp;</span></p>
 <p id="afs">Annual Fuel Savings: <span id="savings">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p><INPUT onclick="return calc(this);" type="submit" value="Submit" name="Submit"> 
<INPUT id="Reset" type="reset" value="Reset" name="Reset"></p>
 </FORM>

 </div>
